metadata.name: Forced mutation
metadata.description: There are many unexplored phenomena in this world. Gifted people feel their individuality and are closest to a sense of inner separation. There is something in each of us that creates a single whole, but it does not always fit together. In the near future, an epidemic of splitting began, when personalities began to separate from each other. Now they will have to exist not only in thoughts, feelings, but also in reality. But can they exist without each other?
